value.0: A wooden pen encloses a stockpile of food - an assortment of mildewy fruit and vegetables, freshly caught fish and other various foodstuffs. The area smells strongly of decay and rot.

This statue depicts an enormous goblin, heavily armoured and armed with a vicious battle-axe. Carved from black stone, its features are marred by poor craftsmanship, but for those knowledgable in the religion of goblinoids it can be recognized as Maglubiyet, the patron deity of goblin-kind.
This old rubble might contain objects from times long past. You will have to search it thoroughly to be sure.
